title: FSX LHSimulations - BUDAPEST LISZT FERENC LHBP V1.01
description:
HOW TO INSTALL


1- Install the scenery.

2- Open regedit and find HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINESOFTWAREWow6432NodeLHSimulationsLHBP
   and add the serial provided into the reg file.

3- Paste the LHBP_objectPlacer.dll into the Modules folder in FSX.

4- Go to Addon Scenery and push LHBP Activator. This will activate your scenery.

5- Run FSX, at the beginning you will get a windows asking to run the LHBP_objectPlacer.dll push YES. After this you will get a problem code, just ignore it.

6-  LHBP is fully working.



Thanks to TIGEROS...

ENJOY!!
